1: Run your postgres DB Docker Instance

2: Create Your Cruddur database with the right Data: 
  - cd into backend-flask `cd backend-flask`
  - Run the Create Database Bash Script `./bin/db-create`
  - Load the Schema `./bin/db-schema-load`
  - Add the Seed Data `./bin/db-seed`


3: You can use this command to connect to the database `./bin/db-connect`

4: Whatever bin file you create you need to give RUN permission use this command `chmod u+x <the-file-path>


